1
00:00:13,280 --> 00:00:16,349
[♪♪♪]

2
00:00:19,971 --> 00:00:21,854
[choking]

3
00:00:23,048 --> 00:00:24,732
The magic Luz's abuela did...

4
00:00:24,809 --> 00:00:26,642
I spoke to Jirou.

5
00:00:26,719 --> 00:00:28,218
I touched him.
He was real.

6
00:00:28,296 --> 00:00:29,904
Give her the baby in this
picture?

7
00:00:29,981 --> 00:00:33,132
The magic only works if the
person in the image is dead.

8
00:00:33,134 --> 00:00:34,283
[crying]

9
00:00:44,645 --> 00:00:46,704
[screams softly]

10
00:00:46,780 --> 00:00:47,779
[baby crying]

11
00:00:47,857 --> 00:00:49,715
Oh. Oh, God.

12
00:00:51,486 --> 00:00:53,219
[humming]

13
00:00:53,916 --> 00:00:58,166
[wind blowing]

14
00:00:58,168 --> 00:01:00,501
[♪♪♪]

15
00:01:29,941 --> 00:01:30,823
[speaking in Japanese]

16
00:01:35,187 --> 00:01:36,120
[laughing in delight]

17
00:02:37,082 --> 00:02:38,891
[♪♪♪]

18
00:03:06,445 --> 00:03:10,097
[distant screaming]

19
00:03:10,099 --> 00:03:11,506
[gasping in fright]

20
00:03:11,508 --> 00:03:15,528
[fireworks crackling outside]

21
00:03:15,530 --> 00:03:17,120
[screaming and cheering outside]

22
00:03:17,122 --> 00:03:19,390
Is it Fourth of July?

23
00:03:21,293 --> 00:03:23,644
No, it's August.

24
00:03:23,646 --> 00:03:24,645
I go look.

25
00:03:24,647 --> 00:03:25,479
No, don't
go out alone.

26
00:03:25,481 --> 00:03:26,939
Wait!
Oh...

27
00:03:28,467 --> 00:03:29,317
Yamato-san...

28
00:03:31,879 --> 00:03:34,071
Yamato-san,
slow down.

29
00:03:35,883 --> 00:03:38,492
[crowds scream and cheer]

30
00:03:44,875 --> 00:03:48,336
[crowds cheer and celebrate]

31
00:03:48,338 --> 00:03:50,654
Hey! Hey, son!

32
00:03:50,656 --> 00:03:52,006
Sonny!

33
00:03:52,008 --> 00:03:53,490
What's going on?

34
00:03:53,492 --> 00:03:54,324
We did it!

35
00:03:54,326 --> 00:03:55,176
What?

36
00:03:55,178 --> 00:03:55,926
We got 'em!

37
00:03:57,013 --> 00:03:58,662
We bombed the Japs!

38
00:03:58,664 --> 00:03:59,697
Whoo!

39
00:03:59,699 --> 00:04:01,891
We hit Hiroshima!

40
00:04:04,002 --> 00:04:05,770
[♪♪♪]

41
00:04:08,191 --> 00:04:10,416
They'll have
to surrender!

42
00:04:10,418 --> 00:04:11,984
[crowd cheering]

43
00:04:15,514 --> 00:04:18,240
[♪♪♪]

44
00:04:25,523 --> 00:04:29,168
[♪♪♪]

45
00:04:49,943 --> 00:04:54,943
Subtitles by explosiveskull
